          "reviewBody": "We are really impressed with the way Ramagya School has maintained its infra!\nThey have well furnished buildings and fully ac classrooms with all the latest equipments. The library is filled with numerous books and things to learn from for all age groups. The school is doing a fantastic job of making sure that they have everything our child needs to learn and grow.\nI'm really glad that I enrolled my child into Ramagya School",
