          },
          "reviewBody": "We're so proud of Ramagya School for their dedication to football sports! Our child has become really good at football and has learned important things like working together in a team, being disciplined, and never giving up. Playing football at school has made our child feel more confident and has helped her become a better, all-around person. We're really thankful for the school for giving our daughter this chance of growing into a career where only boys have the mettle to stay!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
